---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} lang="ko" pathPrefix="/kr">
  {/* HERO */}
  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Quality & Trust</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub md:text-base leading-relaxed">
      고객사 승인·시스템 인증·지식재산 및 사내 시험/검사 설비를 기반으로
      공정 신뢰성과 품질 추적성을 확보합니다.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      {highlights.map((h) => (
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-surface p-5 shadow-soft">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">{h.title}</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub leading-relaxed">{h.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 1) 고객사/인증기관 승인 */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">고객사 / 인증기관 승인</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">외부 공개 시 민감할 수 있는 원본 인증서 대신, 승인 정보만 표로 정리합니다.</p>

    <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-[900px] w-full border-separate border-spacing-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-surface">
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">고객사 / 인증기관</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">인증 사양 및 규격</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">비고 (인증 범위/등급)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {customerApprovals.map((r) => (
            <tr class="bg-base">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white/90 border-b border-stroke">{r.customer}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.spec}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.note}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 2) 시스템/기업 인증 */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">시스템 인증 / 기업 인증</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">품질·환경·자동차 품질 시스템 및 기업 인증을 표로 관리합니다.</p>

    <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-[1100px] w-full border-separate border-spacing-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-surface">
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">구분</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">인증명</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">발급기관</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">유효기간</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">적용 범위</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">비고</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {systemCerts.map((r) => (
            <tr class="bg-base">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white/90 border-b border-stroke">{r.category}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.name}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.issuer}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.validity}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.scope}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.note}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 3) 특허/디자인등록 */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">특허 / 디자인 등록</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">핵심 기술/설비 관련 등록 정보를 표로 정리합니다.</p>

    <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-[950px] w-full border-separate border-spacing-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-surface">
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">구분</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">명칭</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">등록번호</th>
            <th class="text-left text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-3 border-b border-stroke">비고</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {ipList.map((r) => (
            <tr class="bg-base">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white/90 border-b border-stroke">{r.type}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.title}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.no}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sub border-b border-stroke">{r.note}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 4) 시험/검사 장비 (사진 카드 그리드) */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Testing & Inspection Equipment</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">
      사내 시험/검사 설비를 통해 두께·내식·공정성·분석 데이터를 확보하고 품질 신뢰성을 강화합니다.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      {testEquipments.map((e) => (
        <figure class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-surface shadow-soft">
          {/* 이미지 프레임: 과도한 확대 방지 + 선명도 유지 */}
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center bg-base" style="aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;">
            <img
              src={e.src}
              alt={`${e.name} (${e.en})`}
              class="h-full w-full object-contain"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>

          <figcaption class="p-3">
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">{e.name}</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-white/60">{e.en}</div>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ESG */}
  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-stroke bg-base p-6 shadow-soft">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">ESG</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sub">
      친환경 3가크롬 등 규제 대응 공정 운영과 시스템 기반 관리를 통해 ESG 경영을 실천합니다.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
